00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Cer=
tificate of Dumb Investment</a>, which would replace the US Securities and =
Exchange Commission=E2=80=99s current=C2=A0regime of =E2=80=9Caccredited in=
vestors=E2=80=9D with a simpler one. You sign a form saying:</p><blockquote=
><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I want to buy a dumb investment. I understand=
 that the person selling it will almost certainly steal all my money, and t=
hat I would almost certainly be better off just buying index funds, but I w=
ant to do this dumb thing anyway. I agree that I will never, under any circ=
umstances, complain to anyone when this investment inevitably goes wrong. I=
 understand that violating this agreement is a felony.</p></blockquote><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And then you take it to an SEC employee, =E2=80=9C=
who slaps you hard across the face and says =E2=80=98really???=E2=80=99=E2=
=80=9D And if you say =E2=80=9Cyes, really,=E2=80=9D then you get the certi=
ficate, and you can invest in whatever you want to, but if you then lose al=
l of your money you are not allowed to complain.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16p=
x 0;">The form, to be clear, is the least important part of this. Virtually=
 any dumb investment will require you to sign a form saying =E2=80=9CI unde=
rstand that this investment is risky and I could lose all my money, but I=
=E2=80=99m oh so smart and daring and I am not bothered by that.=E2=80=9D A=
nyone would sign that! That=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>marketing</em>.=C2=A0Who doe=
sn=E2=80=99t want to be sophisticated? No, the important parts are:</p><ol =
style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09=
<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Slapping you beforehand, and</li>=09<li s=
tyle=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Not allowing you to complain afterwards.</li><=
/ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/35465286.256336/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGVsZWdyYXBoLmNvLnVrL=
21vbmV5L2JhbmtpbmcvY3VycmVudC1hY2NvdW50cy9yZXZvbHV0LWFza3Mtc3VzcGVjdGVkLXNj=
